The Unveiling Of The BBI Report Appears To Have Set A Stage For High Voltage Politics Ahead Of The 2022 General Elections. And Now The Orange Democratic Movement, ODM Party, Wants The Country To Adopt A Parliamentary System Of Government With A Powerful Prime Minister And 2 Deputies. And While A Host Of Leaders Are Pushing For A Referendum, Deputy President William Ruto Is Vehemently Opposing That Route, Which He Claims Is A Scheme For Some People To Cling To Power.